prompts.user:
Live-model eval task. You are given the agentic-mermaid Code Mode contract: synchronous JavaScript body only; global mermaid.* SDK; no async/await; parse, narrow, mutate, verify, inspect verify.ok/warnings before serialize; SDK results are read-only. Return ONLY executable JavaScript body, no markdown. Task ID er_add_order. Input Mermaid: erDiagram
  CUSTOMER {
    string id
  }. Task: add an ORDER entity with string id using structured mutation, verify, then serialize.

rawResponse:
const r0 = mermaid.parseMermaid('erDiagram\n  CUSTOMER {\n    string id\n  }')
if (!r0.ok) return { phase: 'parse', errors: r0.error }

const er = mermaid.asEr(r0.value)
if (!er) return { phase: 'narrow', kind: r0.value.kind }

const r1 = mermaid.mutate(er, { kind: 'add_entity', id: 'ORDER', attributes: ['string id'] })
if (!r1.ok) return { phase: 'mutate', error: r1.error }

const verify = mermaid.verifyMermaid(r1.value)
const ok = verify.ok
const warnings = verify.warnings
if (!ok) return { phase: 'verify', warnings: warnings }

return { source: mermaid.serializeMermaid(r1.value) }

